The JavaTM XML Pack is an all-in-one download of Java technologies for XML. Bundling 
the Java XML technologies together into a Java XML Pack ensures developers of a quick
and easy development cycle for integration of XML into the Java platform. The Java XML
Pack includes current, publicly-available releases of Java APIs and Architectures for 
XML.

The Java XML Pack Summer 02 Update Release includes the following:
  * Java API for XML Messaging (JAXM) v1.1_01
  * Java API for XML Processing (JAXP) v1.2_01
  * Java API for XML Registries (JAXR) v1.0_02
  * Java API for XML-based RPC (JAX-RPC) v1.0_01
  * SOAP with Attachments API for Java (SAAJ) v1.1_02

